name: Granny cushion - Pillow cover
description:
The Granny pillow cover brings you back to the lovely days of the hand crocheted pillows. My updated version is a hand screenprinted cushion made on high-quality canvas using water based inks environmentally friendly. The Granny pillow cover is provided with a zip so that you can easily wash it. The back side is plain.

The printing has been properly fixed and the fabric washed to avoid from shrinking.

This listing is for one Granny pillow cover. It does NOT INCLUDE THE INSERT (it is also available with the insert. Please, check my shop if you want it with the insert).

It is available in four colors: russet, turquoise, dark blue and mustard yellow.

See all colours at www.etsy.com/shop/olula

Care instructions: Hand wash in cold water. Do not iron the print.

Measures: 13" x 13" (33 cm x 33 cm).
